title: Google\Cloud\DocumentAI\V1\CreateProcessorRequest
name: CreateProcessorRequest
description:
Request message for create a processor. Notice this request is sent to a regionalized backend service, and if the processor type is not available on that region, the creation will fail.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.documentai.v1.CreateProcessorRequest

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The parent (project and location) under which to create the processor. Format: projects/{project}/locations/{location}

params.name: data.processor
params.description: Required. The processor to be created, requires [processor_type] and [display_name] to be set. Also, the processor is under CMEK if CMEK fields are set.
